lcoming feeling? How is that achieved? What is the outcome?<br />\n\tThis week's topic: The atmosphere was welcoming... (90-110 words)</p>\n<p>\n\tSuggestions:<br />\n\t1) welcoming speech<br />\n\t2) welcoming dinner<br />\n\t3) welcoming vacation<br />\n\t4) welcoming surprise<br />\n\t5) Instead of writing a scenario, feel free to comment on the story below.</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>范例1：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tWolfe knew he had to wait for a while before he would either see the person he wanted to see, or for him to give up, so then, he leaned back in the sofa and thought about what to say if and when he saw the model. In this sunny afternoon, the large glass walls surrounding the lobby let in the warm sunlight. The entire place gave a very welcoming feeling. Wolfe poked the ice in his drink as he observed the people passing by. Almost all of them walked rather quickly, seemingly carrying a purpose in their steps.</p>\n<p>\n\t想要得到专业主持人的点评和意见吗？<a href=\"http://st.hujiang.com/topic/167827011258/\" target=\"_blank\">快来节目现场一试身手吧&gt;&gt;</a></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p787999/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p787999\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p795313/\">南海仲裁的全面科普：中国一点都不能少！</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p795413/\">BBC把咱们微博上的南海段子都翻成了英文……</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p795411/\">卡梅伦首相的最后一天 离开唐宁街时他说了啥</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p794979/\">王俊凯秒变北京瘫！这个魔性的姿势英文咋说</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p795377/\">龙妈新片《遇见你之前》台词又甜又虐苏哭了</